        {
            "id": 6309744,
            "title": "外資近5日買超個股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>1. 外資累計買超 5 日的股票<br/>群益台灣精選高息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00919:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00919-TW</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)、南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)、復華富時不動產 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00712:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00712\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00712-TW</a>)、國泰永續高股息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00878:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00878\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00878-TW</a>)</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>2. 外資累計買超 4 日的股票<br/>聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)、群益台灣精選高息 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00919:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\